      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      400.15,
      173.83,
      413.11
    ],
    "text": "dated 07.09.2012.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      431.95,
      542.54,
      444.91
    ],
    "text": "According to Clause 9.2.3 therein, to be considered for appointment, an unemployed",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      455.71,
      543.03,
      468.67
    ],
    "text": "graduate must be below 35 years of age. The Petitioner was born on 23.01.1974 and at",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      479.59,
      543.03,
      492.55
    ],
    "text": "the time this application was filed on 24.01.2013, he was 39 years of age. The Respondents",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      503.35,
      542.58,
      516.31
    ],
    "text": "have not impugned the Development Officers Service Minute in these proceedings.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      527.23,
      542.59,
      540.19
    ],
    "text": "Hence, no order can be made directing the Respondents to make permanent the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      550.99,
      541.59,
      563.95
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner as a Development Officer with the completion of his one-year training period.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      582.82,
      542.5,
      595.78
    ],
    "text": "The only question to be determined is whether his release to the Ministry of Public",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      606.58,
      542.83,
      619.54
    ],
    "text": "Administration has infringed his Fundamental Rights guaranteed by Article 12(1) of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      630.46,
      148.99,
      643.42
    ],
    "text": "Constitution.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.66,
      542.56,
      87.62
    ],
    "text": "At the outset it must be observed that the Petitioner did not fit the class of persons to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      98.42,
      542.97,
      111.38
    ],
    "text": "whom employment was to be offered by the Government under the Unemployed",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      122.3,
      542.64,
      135.26
    ],
    "text": "Graduates scheme. He was at the relevant time, holding a permanent post in the SLBC",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      146.06,
      402.6,
      159.02
    ],
    "text": "and an elected member of the Kekirawa Pradeshiya Sabhawa.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      177.86,
      542.68,
      190.82
    ],
    "text": "The contention of the Petitioner is that his release to the Ministry of Public Administration",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      201.62,
      542.85,
      214.58
    ],
    "text": "was due to his involvement in trade union activities. However, it appears that the actual",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      225.5,
      542.55,
      238.46
    ],
    "text": "reason is his application for official leave to attend a meeting of the Kekirawa Pradeshiya",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      249.29,
      542.93,
      262.25
    ],
    "text": "Sabhawa at which the budget was to be debated and approved. The official leave was",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      271.94,
      542.87,
      286.13
    ],
    "text": "applied for by letter dated 23.11.2012. The 3rd Respondent on receiving this request",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      296.93,
      542.97,
      309.89
    ],
    "text": "approved only personal leave and refused to grant permission for official leave. Thereafter,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      319.46,
      543.02,
      333.65
    ],
    "text": "by letter dated 26.11.2012, the 3rd Respondent sought the views of the 1st Respondent as",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.57,
      304.9,
      357.53
    ],
    "text": "to how such requests are to be considered.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      375.14,
      542.72,
      389.33
    ],
    "text": "Thereupon, the 1st Respondent by letter dated 19.12.2012 wrote to the Secretary, Ministry",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      400.15,
      542.96,
      413.11
    ],
    "text": "of Public Administration and Home Affairs informing that the Petitioner is released to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      423.91,
      542.97,
      436.87
    ],
    "text": "Ministry to be transferred to the District Secretariat of Anuradhapura. The following",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      447.79,
      255.7,
      460.75
    ],
    "text": "reasons were given for this action:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      477.58,
      542.91,
      492.55
    ],
    "text": "(1) The Petitioner has to take part at various meetings within the Kekirawa Pradeshiya",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      503.35,
      187.9,
      516.31
    ],
    "text": "Sabhawa area.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      525.22,
      543.0,
      540.19
    ],
    "text": "(2) Due to his responsibilities as a Member of the Kekirawa Pradeshiya Sabhawa and",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      550.99,
      542.91,
      563.95
    ],
    "text": "the need to obtain leave to attend to matters connected therewith, his maximum",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      574.78,
      453.15,
      587.74
    ],
    "text": "participation is not possible with the work as a Graduate Trainee.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      596.65,
      542.49,
      611.62
    ],
    "text": "(3) There is no provision for granting of leave of this nature during the period of",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      622.42,
      154.87,
      635.38
    ],
    "text": "training.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      644.17,
      489.51,
      659.14
    ],
    "text": "(4) The conduct of the Petitioner is disruptive to the work of other officers.",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.66,
      542.87,
      87.62
    ],
    "text": "The version of the Respondents is somewhat corroborated by the counter affidavit of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      97.19,
      543.03,
      111.38
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner. He states that when he arrived at the Ministry of Public Administration, the 2nd",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      122.3,
      542.65,
      135.26
    ],
    "text": "Respondent informed him that he need not come there and that if the Petitioner wished,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      146.06,
      542.95,
      159.02
    ],
    "text": "arrangements could be made for the Petitioner to go to the District of Anuradhapura even",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      168.59,
      542.87,
      182.78
    ],
    "text": "the next day. However, the Petitioner states that the 2nd Respondent treated him with",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      193.7,
      353.4,
      206.66
    ],
    "text": "utmost disrespect when he met him on 04.01.2013.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      225.5,
      542.97,
      238.46
    ],
    "text": "This evidence of the Petitioner is belated and lacks probative value. The Petitioner filed an",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      249.29,
      542.55,
      262.25
    ],
    "text": "affidavit incorrectly dated 24.01.2012 (the petition is dated 24.01.2013) along with his",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      273.17,
      543.03,
      286.13
    ],
    "text": "petition. However, there is no mention therein of the alleged meeting on 04.01.2013",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      296.93,
      542.8,
      309.89
    ],
    "text": "although it was a critical part of his case. It is only in his counter affidavit has the Petitioner",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      320.69,
      191.86,
      333.65
    ],
    "text": "taken up this position.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      351.26,
      542.96,
      365.45
    ],
    "text": "This has deprived the 2nd Respondent of an opportunity of meeting the allegations made",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      376.37,
      542.99,
      389.33
    ],
    "text": "by the Petitioner. Counter affidavits should not be a mode of presenting new evidence by",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      400.15,
      542.99,
